52:18.680 --> 52:28.774
[SPEAKER_74]: Catlin represents Ireland in Southern California, Arizona, Hawaii, Nevada, New Mexico, and Utah, but most importantly to us in Los Angeles.

52:28.923 --> 52:39.073
[SPEAKER_74]: I'm honored to be joined also by, this is a great, great honor, colleagues, to be joined by Verona Murphy, Ireland's Keon Corla.

