52:53.236 --> 53:01.292
[SPEAKER_74]: And Verona became the first woman in the history of the Republic of Ireland to hold this office, and she was elected in 2024.

53:06.588 --> 53:07.750
[SPEAKER_74]: And she is just a delight.

53:07.830 --> 53:10.774
