53:16.141 --> 53:18.844
[SPEAKER_74]: So we are honored by Speaker Verona Murphy.

53:27.236 --> 53:33.805
[SPEAKER_21]: Members of City Council, ladies and gentlemen, thank you for the warm welcome here in Los Angeles City Hall.

53:34.746 --> 53:35.667
[SPEAKER_21]: It's a great honor.

53:36.406 --> 53:43.513
[SPEAKER_21]: to visit this remarkable city on behalf of the Irish state, and to bring you greetings from the Irish community.

53:44.614 --> 53:54.985
[SPEAKER_21]: Los Angeles and Ireland may be separated by thousands of miles, but we are connected by our people, our shared history, and our existing values.

53:56.486 --> 54:02.953
[SPEAKER_21]: For generations, Irish men and women have made their home in this city, and all across California.

54:03.710 --> 54:10.638
[SPEAKER_21]: They've helped build communities, businesses, and institutions that come to shape Los Angeles today.

54:11.820 --> 54:19.489
[SPEAKER_21]: In turn, this city has embraced the Irish people and their culture, our literature, our music, and our dance.

54:20.990 --> 54:27.038
[SPEAKER_21]: Today, we're so proud of the Irish making their mark on Los Angeles and its creative industries.

54:27.638 --> 54:33.345
[SPEAKER_21]: And we will be cheering on our many nominees at the Oscars this coming Sunday.

54:34.456 --> 54:40.230
[SPEAKER_21]: Cities like Los Angeles remind us of the strength that comes from diversity and openness.

54:41.012 --> 54:51.537
[SPEAKER_21]: This is a city built on talent from every corner of the world, which demonstrates what can be achieved when communities work together with imagination and ambition.

54:52.664 --> 54:59.052
[SPEAKER_21]: In Ireland, our parliament, the Oireachtas, has long valued international friendships.

54:59.973 --> 55:10.787
[SPEAKER_21]: Parliamentary diplomacy and exchanges between governments, cities, and civic leaders play a very important role in strengthening those relationships.

55:11.428 --> 55:22.182
[SPEAKER_21]: I also happen to be the convener of the Irish-American Friendship Group, of which we have the largest membership of 190 friendship groups.

55:23.495 --> 55:34.169
[SPEAKER_21]: But visits such as this one help us learn from one another, shared experiences, which deepen the bonds that already exist between our people.

55:35.171 --> 55:41.479
[SPEAKER_21]: Ireland today is a modern, outward-looking country with strong ties to the United States.

55:42.340 --> 55:46.065
[SPEAKER_21]: Millions of Americans proudly claim Irish ancestry.

55:47.007 --> 55:53.215
[SPEAKER_21]: And here in LA, that connection is especially visible in the arts and the businesses

55:53.431 --> 55:54.413
