01:53:04.422 --> 01:53:10.893
[SPEAKER_90]: Right there, and I'm trying to fill the shoes and support the legacy and make sure it goes onwards.

01:53:11.374 --> 01:53:18.345
[SPEAKER_90]: And today, all of you and your words and what you embody just remind us to be courageous in this moment.

01:53:19.147 --> 01:53:27.561
