01:55:07.255 --> 01:55:11.621
[SPEAKER_63]: I think this full house is a recognition of what you brought for this city, so thank you very much.

01:55:13.163 --> 01:55:13.683
[SPEAKER_76]: Thank you so much.

01:55:13.743 --> 01:55:14.604
[SPEAKER_76]: Council Member Hutt.

01:55:17.188 --> 01:55:31.025
[SPEAKER_60]: Thank you, Mr. President, and thank you, Council Member Hernandez, for really bringing someone that is a titan to our council, and recognizing him, and then bringing a street name after him.

01:55:31.065 --> 01:55:33.729
[SPEAKER_60]: You're doing a square name after him.

01:55:34.470 --> 01:55:37.093
[SPEAKER_60]: Because our children need to know what your work is.

01:55:37.478 --> 01:55:40.681
