01:56:03.943 --> 01:56:05.545
[SPEAKER_60]: I think it'll be pretty exciting.

01:56:06.014 --> 01:56:08.599
[SPEAKER_60]: And I just want to thank you for the work you've done.

01:56:08.759 --> 01:56:14.610
[SPEAKER_60]: And thank your family for sharing you with our city and with our state.

01:56:14.630 --> 01:56:15.232
