02:20:54.551 --> 02:20:55.373
[SPEAKER_18]: Let's lift them up.

02:20:55.613 --> 02:20:57.057
[SPEAKER_18]: And who cares who they're doing it for?

02:20:57.418 --> 02:21:00.646
[SPEAKER_18]: Let's just make sure that we're all doing that work together and meeting each other with grace.

02:21:00.826 --> 02:21:01.969
[SPEAKER_18]: So thank you both so much.

02:21:06.016 --> 02:21:09.521
[SPEAKER_90]: Thank you so much, Reverend Hoover, for your leadership and your service.

02:21:09.941 --> 02:21:13.246
[SPEAKER_90]: And our city is just so much stronger because of you.

02:21:13.286 --> 02:21:15.950
[SPEAKER_90]: And you put it so well.

02:21:16.150 --> 02:21:20.175
[SPEAKER_90]: And so now I want to pass it back to Council President in case there are any members on the queue.

