[SPEAKER_60]: I have to hand, right?

02:21:29.148 --> 02:21:34.555
[SPEAKER_60]: So I want to thank you, both Council Member Soto-Martinez and Council Member

02:21:34.990 --> 02:21:45.064
[SPEAKER_60]: for taking the time to really look at LA Voice and Reverend Zach for the work that he's done.

02:21:45.124 --> 02:21:46.646
[SPEAKER_60]: He's a unifier.

02:21:47.407 --> 02:21:48.489
[SPEAKER_60]: He's an organizer.

02:21:49.190 --> 02:21:55.699
[SPEAKER_60]: And he definitely, in my experience, sees the value of what happens neighborhood by neighborhood.

02:21:55.848 --> 02:21:59.775
[SPEAKER_60]: So I just want to thank you for taking this time to acknowledge him.

02:21:59.795 --> 02:22:01.899
[SPEAKER_60]: And have a great spring break.

02:22:02.359 --> 02:22:03.922
[SPEAKER_60]: You came on the perfect day, right?

02:22:04.523 --> 02:22:06.707
