02:22:08.190 --> 02:22:10.754
[SPEAKER_60]: So thank you so much for honoring him today.

02:22:10.914 --> 02:22:11.275
[SPEAKER_60]: Thanks.

02:22:15.102 --> 02:22:36.013
[SPEAKER_76]: Thank you so much Council Member Soto-Martinez and Council Member Jurado for organizing this recognition and having it fall on our St. Patrick's Day celebration for one of our favorite Irishmen here in the city of Los Angeles and a great leader and somebody who's dedicated

02:22:36.803 --> 02:22:39.747
[SPEAKER_76]: I think we might have an objection on the floor, Zach.

02:22:45.435 --> 02:22:51.804
[SPEAKER_76]: But thank you for the opportunity to recognize your work and bringing your family and friends here with you.

02:22:51.844 --> 02:22:54.808
[SPEAKER_76]: I think there's a lot to say about everything you've done.

02:22:54.868 --> 02:22:57.952
[SPEAKER_76]: I will pay you an extremely personal compliment.

02:22:58.012 --> 02:23:02.018
[SPEAKER_76]: It's probably one of the highest compliments I can pay to anybody.

02:23:04.201 --> 02:23:05.983
[SPEAKER_76]: My mother called me one Friday.

02:23:06.689 --> 02:23:11.465
[SPEAKER_76]: and asked if I could come to service that weekend.

02:23:12.408 --> 02:23:18.167
[SPEAKER_76]: And she said, yeah, you should come because Zack and LA Voice are going to be speaking during service.

02:23:19.075 --> 02:23:21.718
[SPEAKER_76]: And I was like, mom, you don't let me speak during service.

02:23:22.879 --> 02:23:31.009
[SPEAKER_76]: So who is this Zach, and how did he get so familiar with the parishioners at your congregation?

02:23:31.089 --> 02:23:35.874
[SPEAKER_76]: But that is the kind of confidence you build all over the city in communities of faith.

02:23:36.275 --> 02:23:40.840
[SPEAKER_76]: And creating the pathway, which is not a small thing at all.

02:23:41.240 --> 02:23:42.802
[SPEAKER_76]: We take it for granted in this city.

02:23:43.263 --> 02:23:47.007
[SPEAKER_76]: But creating the pathway for people of faith

02:23:47.392 --> 02:23:52.999
[SPEAKER_76]: to engage in political struggle, as crazy as our political life is in this country.

02:23:53.639 --> 02:24:00.347
