02:36:47.337 --> 02:36:56.031
[SPEAKER_12]: as an influence, the kind of influence that I hold strong and that I hold dear in my heart to lead my son.

02:36:56.532 --> 02:37:06.607
[SPEAKER_12]: And I am incredibly grateful that he is his coach for this year and not only this year, but as he goes through his life.

02:37:06.708 --> 02:37:12.036
[SPEAKER_12]: I'm sure that Dylan will be around to champion Aiden as he moves forward in his life.

02:37:12.116 --> 02:37:14.560
[SPEAKER_12]: So Dylan, thank you, brother.

02:37:20.463 --> 02:37:31.063
[SPEAKER_51]: When you look at what this team went through last year, losing their field, their school, their equipment, their homes, their town.

02:37:33.237 --> 02:37:44.997
[SPEAKER_51]: Having a perfect season really says something about the quality of the leadership that Coach Smith brings to this team and these incredible young men.

02:37:45.057 --> 02:37:52.950
[SPEAKER_51]: So it is now my honor to recognize Coach Dylan Smith with the Certificate of Recognition on behalf

02:37:53.892 --> 02:38:05.740
