02:41:46.652 --> 02:41:49.276
[SPEAKER_68]: And Stu is a parent and also one of our board members.

02:41:49.396 --> 02:41:52.721
[SPEAKER_68]: And they were bringing water every day, equipment.

02:41:52.901 --> 02:41:56.847
