02:42:05.380 --> 02:42:27.017
[SPEAKER_68]: You know Aiden's here to represent the players and obviously I wouldn't be standing up here without you know that the kids They're literal blood sweat and tears that they left on the field To have a perfect season and every single one of those kids did it for the community They could have transferred they could have left they could have went to other schools they all said they wanted to stay here and do it for Palisades and

02:42:26.997 --> 02:42:36.007
[SPEAKER_68]: That's why I wake up every morning and lose sleep and watch film and whatever I have to do to make sure these kids succeed in life and on the football field.

02:42:36.027 --> 02:42:40.351
[SPEAKER_68]: So thank you everybody and I appreciate this.

02:42:40.371 --> 02:42:41.132
[SPEAKER_76]: Thank you so much.

02:42:42.594 --> 02:42:43.895
[SPEAKER_51]: Thank you, Council President.

02:42:44.255 --> 02:42:44.616
[SPEAKER_76]: All right.

02:42:45.577 --> 02:42:50.642
[SPEAKER_76]: We'll move to our next presentation brought to us by Council District 1 and 13.

02:42:58.115 --> 02:43:13.626
Okay.

02:43:34.193 --> 02:43:45.875
[SPEAKER_72]: Thank you.

02:43:46.115 --> 02:43:56.134
[SPEAKER_12]: Thank you.

02:43:58.139 --> 02:43:58.681
[SPEAKER_36]: Hello.

02:43:58.741 --> 02:43:59.664
[SPEAKER_36]: Good morning, everyone.

