02:53:08.178 --> 02:53:12.086
[SPEAKER_17]: One in three new educators leave the profession within the first five years.

02:53:12.707 --> 02:53:17.397
[SPEAKER_17]: And almost a third of UTLA members work a second job just to make ends meet.

02:53:17.377 --> 02:53:23.848
[SPEAKER_17]: This is not even, I mean it used to be, we used to complain that LA Unified educators couldn't afford to buy a home in LA.

