05:47:13.814 --> 05:47:22.988
[SPEAKER_06]: It is with a heavy heart that I ask to adjourn today's council meeting in honor of Juan Cuevas, who was tragically taken from us due to gun violence at the age of 26.

05:47:23.845 --> 05:47:35.138
