05:47:45.296 --> 05:47:50.324
[SPEAKER_06]: He loved to laugh and to make others laugh, something that is sorely missed by his family, friends, and loved ones.

05:47:51.045 --> 05:47:59.539
[SPEAKER_06]: Juan was shot and killed by an unknown assailant January 9th, 2019, near Beverly Boulevard and St. Andrew's Place at the edge of Koreatown.

05:48:00.346 --> 05:48:10.480
